(1232, 'en', NULL, 'phpfox', NULL, 'setting_google_api_key', '<title>Google API Key</title><info>Google offers many services that require an API key (like the Places service), enter your Google API key here.\r\n\r\nMore information on how to get an API key can be found <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/tutorial#api_key\">here</a>.</info>', '<title>Google API Key</title><info>Google offers many services that require an API key (like the Places service), enter your Google API key here.\r\n\r\nMore information on how to get an API key can be found <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/tutorial#api_key\">here</a>.</info>', 1644850817),
