(10837, 'en', NULL, 'phpfox', NULL, 'setting_v_pf_video_mux_webhook_signing_secret', '<title>Mux Webhook Signing Secret</title><info><b>Mux Webhook Signing Secret</b> is required for Videos app if your are using Mux as Uploading Method.<br/>You must add a webhook to your Mux project, if you doesn\'t have one, just go to this <a href=\"https://dashboard.mux.com/settings/webhooks\">Link</a> and create a new webhook.<br/>Add URL <a href=\"video/mux-callback/?sessionid=620a6f6d3a4a0\">video/mux-callback/?sessionid=620a6f6d3a4a0</a> to <b>URL to notify</b> field then save it.<br/>After you got a webhook, copy <b>Signing Secret</b> and paste to this setting.</info>', '<title>Mux Webhook Signing Secret</title><info><b>Mux Webhook Signing Secret</b> is required for Videos app if your are using Mux as Uploading Method.<br/>You must add a webhook to your Mux project, if you doesn\'t have one, just go to this <a href=\"https://dashboard.mux.com/settings/webhooks\">Link</a> and create a new webhook.<br/>Add URL <a href=\"video/mux-callback/?sessionid=620a6f6d3a4a0\">video/mux-callback/?sessionid=620a6f6d3a4a0</a> to <b>URL to notify</b> field then save it.<br/>After you got a webhook, copy <b>Signing Secret</b> and paste to this setting.</info>', 1644851053),
